@host = http://localhost:5000
@tenantId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@token = {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### 登录获取 token（可复用现有登录请求）
# @name login
POST {{host}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "P@ssw0rd!"
}

### 创建迁移任务
# @name createTask
POST {{host}}/api/v1/app-migrations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Idempotency-Key: app-migration-create-001

{
  "appInstanceId": "10001",
  "readOnlyWindow": true,
  "enableDualWrite": false,
  "enableRollback": true
}

### 显式修复主绑定（混合模式）
POST {{host}}/api/v1/app-migrations/repair-primary-binding
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Idempotency-Key: app-migration-repair-binding-001

{
  "appInstanceId": "10001"
}

### 查询任务列表（items[].schemaRepairLog：SQLite 结构/容灾自修复摘要，执行 start 或 recover 后写入）
GET {{host}}/api/v1/app-migrations?pageIndex=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 预检查
POST {{host}}/api/v1/app-migrations/{{createTask.response.body.data.id}}/precheck
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Idempotency-Key: app-migration-precheck-001

### 启动迁移
POST {{host}}/api/v1/app-migrations/{{createTask.response.body.data.id}}/start
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Idempotency-Key: app-migration-start-001

### 查询进度
GET {{host}}/api/v1/app-migrations/{{createTask.response.body.data.id}}/progress
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 完整性校验
POST {{host}}/api/v1/app-migrations/{{createTask.response.body.data.id}}/validate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Idempotency-Key: app-migration-validate-001

### 切换到应用独立库
POST {{host}}/api/v1/app-migrations/{{createTask.response.body.data.id}}/cutover
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Idempotency-Key: app-migration-cutover-001

{
  "enableReadOnlyWindow": true,
  "enableDualWrite": false
}

### 回切到主库
POST {{host}}/api/v1/app-migrations/{{createTask.response.body.data.id}}/rollback
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Idempotency-Key: app-migration-rollback-001

### 失败任务重置（可重试）
POST {{host}}/api/v1/app-migrations/{{createTask.response.body.data.id}}/reset
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Idempotency-Key: app-migration-reset-001

### 失败任务容灾恢复（自动重置 + 重跑；SkipIdempotency，无需 Idempotency-Key）
POST {{host}}/api/v1/app-migrations/{{createTask.response.body.data.id}}/recover
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
